1. Check AWS CLI configuration : aws configure
2. Check configured identity : aws sts get-caller-identity
3. List S3 buckets : aws s3 ls 
4. Create S3 bucket : aws s3 mb s3://my-devops-bucket
5. Upload file to S3 : aws s3 cp file.txt s3://my-devops-bucket/
6. Download file from S3 : aws s3 cp s3://my-devops-bucket/file.txt .
7. Delete file from S3 : aws s3 rm s3://my-devops-bucket/file.txt
8. List EC2 instances : aws ec2 describe-instances
9. Start EC2 instance : aws ec2 start-instances --instance-ids i-1234567890
10. Stop EC2 instance : aws ec2 stop-instances --instance-ids i-1234567890
11. Create key pair : aws ec2 create-key-pair --key-name mykey
12. List IAM users : aws iam list-users
1️3. Create IAM user : aws iam create-user --user-name devops-user
14. List Lambda functions : aws lambda list-functions
15. List CloudWatch alarms : aws cloudwatch describe-alarms
16. List VPCs : aws ec2 describe-vpcs
